            <title>[LU-15382] ASSERTION(!cfs_hash_with_assert_empty(hs)) failed: hash lu_site_osd-ldi bucket is not empty</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15382</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The LCTL command &quot;cfg_device&quot; is obsolete and some operations (such as &quot;cleanup&quot;, &quot;detach&quot;) don&apos;t support it anymore. In mds_survey and lfsck-performance it causes the echo client device not to be destroyed and causes LBUG when umounting the related Lustre device.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
